title: California Gets Break From Storms Ahead of New Year’s Eve Rain
description: California is in for a brief weekend reprieve from damaging holiday storms that killed four people and hobbled Christmas travel, but weather officials warned of more wet weather heading to the rain-soaked state starting on New Year’s Eve.
